ade to calculate start with total shares outstanding and subtract the number of restricted shares restricted stock typically is that issued to company insiders with limits on when it may be traded dividend yield a companys dividend expressed as a percentage of its current stock price key stock data pe ratio ttm na eps ttm  market cap  m shares outstanding  m public float  m yield thm has not issued dividends in more than  year latest dividend na exdividend date na  shares sold short the total number of shares of a security that have been sold short and not yet repurchased change from last percentage change in short interest from the previous report to the most recent report exchanges report short interest twice a month percent of float total short positions relative to the number of shares available to trade short interest  shares sold short  change from last  percent of float   money flow uptickdowntick ratio money flow measures the relative buying and selling pressure on a stock based on the value of trades made on an uptick in price and the value of trades made on a downtick in price the updown ratio is calculated by dividing the value of uptick trades by the value of downtick trades net money flow is the value of uptick trades minus the value of downtick trades our calculations are based on comprehensive delayed quotes stock money flow uptickdowntick trade ratio    net money flow   money flow gives a snapshot of relative buying and selling pressure in a stock a ratio above one suggests greater buying pressure below one suggests greater selling advertisement competitors thm company change pe ttm aem agnico eagle mines ltd    ng novagold resources inc    sa seabridge gold inc    au anglogold ashanti ltd adr    cdu cardero resource corp    rbycf rubicon minerals corp    more information on thm competitor data provided by capital cube profile thm international tower hill mines ltd is a mineral exploration company which engages in the acquisition and exploration of m